{
  "stem": "942.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This, this was burning for days, because, you know, all this compressed paper, you know, did not burn too well.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So somebody was tending it and kept pouring stuff on it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And you know, the crematoriums were all blown up in November.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So there were no more gassing and cremation, because they did not want to leave any evidence behind.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I did not.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was in Auschwitz, and that was in Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was in Auschwitz I, and that was in Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the transports were leaving.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Two transports have left, and they were gathering all the people from the satellite camps into Auschwitz, to where I was.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I recognized some, a couple of my friends from my town.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were brought in from a place called [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were working in coal mines.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were all black from this coal dust, and they were just sick.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They couldn't walk anymore.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were laying down in this barrack.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I told them, look, you have to get up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was getting ready to go with this transport, because I had to make a choice whether I'm going to stay or whether I'm going to leave, you know.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I knew that before the SS leave, they'll blow up the whole camp, or they'll shoot everybody, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was, I didn't want to take that chance to stay on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And these people, they couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I was in, not in such a bad shape, you know, at that time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they said no, we're not, we're staying, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so I went on this death march-- so-called death march.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
